# Demo: Tool Usage
# Shows file reading, grep, and shell command execution

Output docs/images/demo-tools.gif

Set Shell "pwsh"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 30ms
Set Padding 20

Type "jdai --new --dangerously-skip-permissions"
Enter
Sleep 5s

Type "Read the first 10 lines of Program.cs and search for all TODO comments in the codebase"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 15s

Screenshot docs/images/demo-tools.png
Sleep 2s
